*** Joe Kari's Todo list ***

Lots of game rcon command:
/slap		slightly hurt someone, as a warning instead of kicking it
/forcespec	force someone to go to spec, usefull to prevent AFK in round-based game
/forceteam	force someone to go to a specific team
/adjustmoney	give or take money: intended for third party rcon script special game (bounty hunter, poker, ...)



